tags.description: The park’s amenities include soccer fields, a picnic pavilion, tennis courts, a basketball court, a beach volleyball court, a playground, small picnic shelters, a nature trail, and a concessions/restrooms building.
tags.name: Swansboro Municipal Park

tags.description: Pirates Den Park is a .62-acre play area located at the junction of Broad Street and Shore Drive, just one block off NC 24 in the Edgewater Heights neighborhood. The park includes an outstanding, nautically-themed playground designed for smaller children.
tags.name: Pirates Den Park
